    "en": {
      "title": "02 with 10 kg of ice",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Army managed to arrest two persons who were transporting 10.4 kg of ice drug in Mannar.",
        "Army intelligence of the 54th Infantry Division who were on duty at the Army Mannar roadblock while transporting 10.4 kg of ice drug in a cab from Thalaimannar to Wankalai through the Mannar army roadblock today (31st) around 06.15 The members and 11th Artillery soldiers arrested and handed over the drugs, the cab and the suspects to the Mannar Police for further investigation."
      ],
